sg":"商業社會返工返學咁忙,賞月呢D又晒時間又無實際意義既野唔做都罷.."},{"pid":"3bb7b447a75eeab3b48b7e9c7ad9a883aff13414","tid":836382,"uid":11973,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣中秋前一個禮拜已經開始搜羅蠟燭燈籠月餅盒<br />\n八月十四迎月放咗學已經落咗樓下玩啦<br />\n未天黑都已經煲緊蠟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天黑返完屋企食飯約埋隔籬屋落去再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中秋前後起碼玩三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上以前比較有節日氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過時過節啲大人都唔會管咁多<br />\n<br />\n而家啲細路又要溫書做功課<br />\n做完又要俾啲怪獸家長捉去補習<br />\n唔補習都要去上興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得嗰一日假又要做假期功課<br />\n啲靚仔想夜瞓啲都驚佢第二朝冇精神趕schedule啦<br />\n食完晚飯仲想落街追月玩燈籠咁happy?<br />\n玩手指都冇時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338757eec3558ae1d65420e83c32beb61b6f8606","tid":836382,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"中秋節日氣氛不復以往，放假都係食飯訓覺等聽日返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3619a884851c46d4c70030b989e28285a72c0fe1","tid":836382,"uid":56321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3bb7b447a75eeab3b48b7e9c7ad9a883aff13414","tid":836382,"uid":11973,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣中秋前一個禮拜已經開始搜羅蠟燭燈籠月餅盒<br />\n八月十四迎月放咗學已經落咗樓下玩啦<br />\n未天黑都已經煲緊蠟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天黑返完屋企食飯約埋隔籬屋落去再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中秋前後起碼玩三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上以前比較有節日氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過時過節啲大